<subSubSection pageId="75" pageNumber="833" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="75.[718,1320,1968,2395]" pageId="75" pageNumber="833">
Specific name was originally spelled albogulttatus but subsequently corrected to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="J. A. Allen" authorityYear="1917" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Glauconycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="75" pageNumber="833" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="alboguttata">alboguttata</taxonomicName>
for gender agreement. A. Hassanin and colleagues in 2018 retrieved 
<taxonomicName authorityName="J. A. Allen" authorityYear="1917" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Glauconycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="75" pageNumber="833" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="alboguttata">G. alboguttata</taxonomicName>
as sister to part of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1913" box="[1036,1145,2243,2276]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Glauconycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="75" pageNumber="833" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="egeria">G. egeria</taxonomicName>
. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
